An explanation…

node.text:
Feeling overwhelmingly honoured to have been asked to be the voice of ‘Mum’ in the new @catsprotection Christmas campaign... Based on the true story of one family and their little cat Casper ... such a magical and sweet tale reminding us of how important it is to microchip your pet... #MakeChristmasMagical and join us on #CaspersMagicalJourney.
Find out more and donate at www.cats.org.uk/caspers-Christmas ... Thank you 🐱

node.text: #shelfie … Summer family reading highlights… Chester recommends @franklampard #frankiesmagicfootball ⚽️ Belle recommends A murder most unladylike series 🕵🏻‍♀️ Harry highly recommends  I, Robot by Peter Crouch, which made him laugh alot 🥅…I’m struggling to choose between two very different reads, The family upstairs @lisajewelluk and The big book of Angels (thank you @seldasoulspace for the recommendation!) … final read of the summer, looking forward to diving headfirst into @celia.walden #Payday which is out tomorrow… full of secrets, twists and turns… #pageturner 📚 🐛… not long till reflections will be on the shelves too😬
